      <title>令人震惊的选举结果结束了博茨瓦纳执政党 58 年的统治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/botswana-s-president-masisi-concedes-defeat-in-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[博茨瓦纳领导人承认失败，因为他的政党在议会选举中遭受重创，这一令人震惊的结果结束了该党对这个钻石​​资源丰富的南部非洲国家 58 年的执政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/botswana-s-president-masisi-concedes-defeat-in-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 06:19:14 GMT</pubDate>
